    {
      "id": "agent-prompting-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Agent / Prompting Nodeset",
      "position": {
        "x": -680,
        "y": 1237
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 300,
      "color": "#1976d2",
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Agent / Prompting Nodeset\n\nTreat this graph as the implementation task surface for locking the v1 agent / prompting nodeset.\n\nCandidate node types:\n- `agent`\n- `prompt`\n- `memory`\n- `tool`\n- `skill`\n- `contract`\n- `task`\n- `observation`\n- `result`\n- `handoff`\n\nCurrent decision:\n- approved in v1: `agent`, `prompt`, `tool`, `contract`, `task`, `observation`, `result`, `handoff`\n- deferred: `memory`\n- not yet a node-type commitment: `skill`\n\nThe value is not just naming AI things. It is making prompt lineage, tool boundaries, and cross-agent work visible.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
