    {
      "id": "agent-prompting-defer-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "V1 Membership Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1180,
        "y": -125
      },
      "width": 400,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## V1 Membership Contract\n\nApproved in v1:\n- `agent`\n- `prompt`\n- `tool`\n- `contract`\n- `task`\n- `observation`\n- `result`\n- `handoff`\n\nDeferred:\n- `memory`\n  - needs stronger scope, retention, and retrieval rules\n\nNot yet a committed node type:\n- `skill`\n  - may be better represented first as tool metadata, graph templates, or reusable contracts\n\nKeep deferred concepts visible as pressures, not as premature commitments.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
