    {
      "id": "agent-prompting-runtime-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Runtime Rules",
      "position": {
        "x": 1660,
        "y": 360
      },
      "width": 460,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Runtime Rules\n\nAgent nodes should not imply unrestricted execution.\n\nCore rules:\n- `contract` bounds what an `agent` may do\n- `tool` use should be explicit, inspectable, and attributable\n- `result` should preserve lineage to prompts and observations\n- `handoff` should preserve responsibility, not erase it\n- memory writes should remain deferred until scope and retention are real\n\nThe runtime value is bounded delegation, not magical autonomy.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
